<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5596&amp;p=82293#p82293"><![CDATA[
So the goal is to avoid the blocks that come at you? I am not too fond of this idea because it removes two things I consider essential: the ability to turn left and right and the freedom to explore.<br /><br />It should be possible to come up with some other kind of gameplay that does not require objects to be placed in the maze... You can have a gun and shooting walls is definitely a possibility, so maybe something interesting can be made with those elements.<br /><br />I do <strong>want</strong> to add objects eventually, but there would be at most 2 or 3 objects in a room, otherwise the speed would drop too much.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Sun Jul 31, 2011 6:01 pm</p><hr />
